4\pi r_{s}^{2}\left[\frac{\Delta P}{L}\frac{\left(\epsilon-h_{c}\right)}{2}\right]=f\left[\left(\rho_{s}-\rho_{f}\right)\frac{4}{3}\pi r_{s}^{3}+\pi r_{s}^{2}\frac{1}{2}\rho_{s}V_{f}^{2}\frac{24}{Re}\right]
